Preliminary work for viewing a stream using ExoPlayer

LitmusPlayer.java - WorldScope's instance of a DASH Stream Player made possible by the ExoPlayer
DashRendererBuilder.java - Contains the stream building logic, converts a mpd resource into a video and audio track renderer playable by LitmusPlayer

ViewActivity.java - Contains basic viewing logic. Instantiates LitmusPlayer and passes the mpd link and the surface from the UI into it for playback later
activity_view.xml - Contains the surface for playback and a button for pausing and playing
